metric_explanations.model_load_time_ms: Time to load model weights from disk to memory/VRAM
metric_explanations.image_prep_time_ms: Time for image loading, color conversion, resizing, etc.
metric_explanations.inference_mean_ms: Average neural network forward pass time, the most important metric
metric_explanations.inference_std_ms: Variance in inference time, lower is more stable
metric_explanations.inference_min_ms: Fastest inference, close to hardware limit
metric_explanations.inference_max_ms: Slowest inference, possibly affected by system scheduling
metric_explanations.fps: Number of CAPTCHAs processable per second, higher is better
metric_explanations.postprocess_time_ms: Time to decode coordinates from model output
metric_explanations.end_to_end_time_ms: Complete processing time including all steps
